-- China Will Maintain Moderately Loose Monetary Policy, Central Bank Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-08T07:56:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-08/china-will-maintain-moderately-loose-monetary-policy-central-bank-says.html

          
          
             China will maintain its moderately
loose monetary policy, the central bank said in a statement on
its website after a quarterly policy meeting. The central bank
said it sees big uncertainties in the global economy.  
